Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:01.58,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,20)}真正的夢想 Chasing Chasing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:06.72,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,超越更多 自己是史上最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:08.72,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,趁現在Chasing Chasing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:14.76,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,如此描繪夢想的自己  胸中之火熊熊燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.23,0:02:23.97,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,奔跑吧 Hero
